[I] A library providing functions commonly found on BSD systems

[T] This library provides useful functions commonly found on BSD systems,
[T] and lacking on others like GNU systems, thus making it easier to port
[T] projects with strong BSD origins, without needing to embed the same code
[T] over and over again on each project.

[U] https://libbsd.freedesktop.org/wiki/

